Method Detail

asUnsignedLongArray

AttrLongArray asUnsignedLongArray()
Casts an array of o_8b to a VERSANT unsigned long (o_u8b ) array. This method can be used with select() and cursorSelect() to enable you to query unsigned data stored in a VERSANT database by an interface other than JVI.

asTimestampArray
